      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=mvb54whyd8]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mvb54whyd8]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ssedmbvn8j]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ssedmbvn8j]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=x25q8z0mip]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=x25q8z0mip]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=vmpp8a1a9n]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vmpp8a1a9n]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gtqph8gvm8]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gtqph8gvm8]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pgq45qm49i]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pgq45qm49i]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gvlr9lwgr6]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gvlr9lwgr6]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ivw0p9dzn3]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ivw0p9dzn3]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=w4s73cwiva]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=w4s73cwiva]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=mdm0eih5pi]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=mdm0eih5pi]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h1 id=\"GuestScenes-FeaturedGuestScene\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"ivw0p9dzn3\">Featured Guest Scene</span></strong></h1><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-banner.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757681451554&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/597491715/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757681451554&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"541\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597098554\" data-linked-resource-version=\"5\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-banner.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"597491715\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"37\" data-media-id=\"81cd3c63-2957-4c00-8340-34cc95bc3771\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757681451554&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=428 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-banner.jpg?version=5&amp;modificationDate=1757681451554&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=214 1x\" /></span><h4 id=\"GuestScenes-Project:TheSmokingGnome\"><span data-colorid=\"w4s73cwiva\">Project</span>: The Smoking Gnome</h4><h4 id=\"GuestScenes-Artist:RémiPerrier\"><span data-colorid=\"mvb54whyd8\">Artist</span>: R&eacute;mi Perrier</h4><p>The Smoking Gnome is a creation of artist <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.remi3d.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">R&eacute;mi Perrier</a> and originated as a school exercise supervised by <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/baptiste-lebouc-44969853\" rel=\"nofollow\">Baptiste Lebouc</a>, where students had to choose a fictional character. R&eacute;mi's ambition was to bring to life an interesting character, with a look that was both enigmatic and captivating, using intentional lighting to emphasize his mysterious personality.</p><hr /><h1 id=\"GuestScenes-MoreFeaturedResources\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"gtqph8gvm8\">More Featured Resources</span></strong></h1></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RU/596770821/The+Smoking+Gnome\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1757679968008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/597491715/smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1757679968008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"600\" data-width=\"600\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"597229619\" data-linked-resource-version=\"3\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"597491715\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"37\" data-media-id=\"7f4991a7-b0a5-49c8-9f23-e64ce86a5069\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1757679968008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=522&amp;height=522 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/597491715/smoking-gnome-thumb.jpg?version=3&amp;modificationDate=1757679968008&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"x25q8z0mip\">The Smoking Gnome</span></strong><br />Maya Project</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/6116474